          "text": "SSRIs\nSNRIs\nBupropion\n[4]\nBuspirone\nTCAs\nLithium\nMirtazapine\nTrazodone\nValproic acid\nMAOIs (should have washout period of 2+ weeks prior to starting a SSRI)\nPhenelzine\nSelegiline\nTranylcypromine",
